{"article_id":"LMmgbvxV8FZ81IY8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"He publicly released 12 pages of emails","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"sent by Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"dealing with racial inequality .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"The documents were marked `` committee confidential ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"-- meaning that only members of the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"( which includes Booker )","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"could have access to them .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"`` I understand the penalty","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"comes with potential ousting from the Senate , ''","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Booker said","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"in making clear","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he planned to break the rules .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"`` I openly invite and accept the consequences of my team","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"releasing that email right now . ''","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"To be clear :","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Booker is n't releasing these emails out of the goodness of his heart","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"or solely because he thinks transparency is critically important","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"when voting on a Supreme Court justice .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"That may well be part of his calculations .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"But the politics of all of this also plays a large part .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Asked afterward about his decision","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to open himself up to possible expulsion from the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Booker made his motivations quite clear :","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"`` A senior senator","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"who is in leadership ,","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"I think","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"he 's the number two in leadership","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"has , in effect , called for my expulsion from the United States Senate","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"and and again I just say ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"'Bring it . '","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"If he wants to go through that process","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"I fully accept responsibility for what I have done ,","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"and again I 'm new in this place .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"This senator has been around a long time .","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"He 's in leadership .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"he was just like a lot of bullies are ,","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"a lot of talk and no action .","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"And so let 's see what he does .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"I 'm willing to accept responsibility for my actions ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"but I do n't know what ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"I do n't know","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"what that senior senator will do . ''","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Booker is talking here about Texas Sen. John Cornyn","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"who is , indeed the second-ranking Republican in the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Cornyn was particularly exercised about Booker 's decision ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"telling the committee","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"that `` running for president is no excuse","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"for violating the rules of the Senate . ...","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"This is no different from the senator","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"deciding to release classified information . ... That is irresponsible and outrageous . ''","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"Cornyn is , without question , right about one thing :","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Booker is very likely running for president .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"And this decision","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"to break the rules","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"is a calculated one","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"aimed at demonstrating","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"that the New Jersey Democrat knows how to fight dirty","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"-- and is willing to do just that against President Donald Trump .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"Go back and read that full quote above from Booker .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Change the `` he '' from Cornyn to Trump .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"Still works , right ?","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"`` I just say ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"'Bring it . ' '' ... `` I think","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"he was just like a lot of bullies are ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"a lot of talk and no action . ''","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"That 's not by accident .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Booker , as well as Sen. Kamala Harris","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"( D-Calif. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"who made her own moment in a clash with Kavanaugh over the special counsel probe","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"being run by Robert Mueller ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"and Sen. Amy Klobuchar","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"( D-Minn. )","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"all understand","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that they are on a very big stage right now .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"All politics is , in part , performance .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"But running for president relies more on performance","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"than running for any other office .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Anyone","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"who has ever considered running for the nation 's top office","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"knows","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that you need to be `` on '' in the big moments ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"show what you are made of","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"when the people are watching .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"And Democratic base voters are VERY much watching this Kavanaugh hearing .","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"They view Trump 's decision","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"to nominate a solid conservative for the seat of swing vote Justice Anthony Kennedy","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"as only the latest in a series of massive affronts","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"committed by Republicans ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"beginning with their total refusal","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"to even meet with Merrick Garland","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"-- President Barack Obama 's nominee","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"to replace the late Antonin Scalia on the court .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"More than 140 people have been arrested","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"for protesting the Kavanaugh hearing on Capitol Hill over the first two days of hearings .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Booker knows","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that one of the biggest complaints from that base about the 2016 election was that Hillary Clinton simply played too nice with Trump .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"She and her campaign tried to stay within the established rules of a campaign .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Trump refused to even acknowledge","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"there were any rules .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Clinton , in the mind of the Democratic base , was fighting","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"with one hand tied behind her back .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"She would never `` go there '' on Trump","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"because she and her team believed","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that getting down in the mud with Trump was a losing proposition","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"-- not to mention those sorts of tactics might do real damage to the health of our political process .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Trump had no such concerns .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and did","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"whatever he believed","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"it took","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"to win .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"He brought a group of women","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"who had accused Bill Clinton of sexual misconduct","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"and sat them in the front row of a presidential debate with Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"He promised","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"he would prosecute her","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"if he was elected president .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"He suggested , repeatedly ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"that her health was failing","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"and that she was simply not up to the demands of the job of president .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"He broke , literally , every rule .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Did so with relish .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"And won .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Which brings us to the positioning of Democrats for 2020","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"-- and what 2018 has taught us about the state of the party .","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"Democratic base voters want not just liberals , but fighters .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez rather than Joe Crowley .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"Andrew Gillum rather than Gwen Graham .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Ayanna Pressley instead of Michael Capuano .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"They want someone","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"who will take the fight to Republicans","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"-- and to Trump in particular .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"Someone","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"who will stand toe-to-toe with Trump","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"and tell him , to his face , why he deserves to be impeached .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Someone","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"not afraid of , well , getting some mud on their shoes .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"Republicans pushed hard on the idea","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"that Booker was not just grandstanding in advance of 2020 ,","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"but was doing so under false pretenses .","depth":7},{"id":141,"text":"Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley 's office insisted","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"the documents","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that Booker made such a show","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"of releasing on Thursday morning","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"had in fact been cleared to be released earlier in the day .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"Booker 's office responded","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"by taking a victory lap ,","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"insisting","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"that he had `` shame [ d ] the committee into agreeing to make last night 's documents publicly available . ''","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"Who has the right in this is hard to tell amid the spin","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"-- and the possibility of miscommunication and mixed signals .","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"But make no mistake :","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"Booker got what he wanted here .","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"Democratic activists wo n't care about the timing of the release of the documents .","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"They will remember Booker staring down the Republican Senate majority and President Trump .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"Remember ,","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"presidential politics is , at times , a performance .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"And Booker gave this one his all .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"What Booker did","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"-- with clear intent --","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"on Thursday morning was to show","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"he 's not going to be cowed by the rules of the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Or by a bully .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"He 's going to say ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"`` Bring it , ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"and get ready to scrap .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"UPDATE :","depth":2},{"id":168,"text":"This story has been updated with a response from Judiciary Committee Chairman Chuck Grassley 's office ,","depth":3},{"id":169,"text":"disputing Booker 's portrayal of his document release","depth":4},{"id":170,"text":"as breaking the Senate 's rules .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":341,"left":337,"right":340,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},